# World Music Map — environment (server-only; never expose via NEXT_PUBLIC_)
#
# Reuses the shared Postgres SERVER as a SEPARATE `world_music_map` database
# (own schema + migrations, not shared tables). Local dev points at the
# docker-compose Postgres on :5433; production points at the Railway Postgres.
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/world_music_map"

# MapTiler tile key (domain-restricted). Optional for the skeleton, which uses
# the keyless MapLibre demo style. Set this when swapping to MapTiler tiles.
# MAPTILER_KEY=""
